  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you see, people have passed on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And many of my friends, you know, have gone, and-- so there's very few that even that you can ask anymore where is this and who was that, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I never thought about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But next time I go to Denmark I definitely would try and get his name, you know, because it was also not an important person in the whole scenario, but he was one that really made it miserable.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we tried a couple of other times to, to get across.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was canceled before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said the water was too choppy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was too many patrol boats out, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But on the 6th-- actually we started on the 5th of October-- we were told there was a place called Dronningmolle.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's like the Queen's Mill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was a little city also of maybe some 100 people, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and they had a big cement factory and roof tile-- those red roof tile-- factory that was lying off the road and then down onto the beach, because that's where they stored all the big pipes and cement blocks and everything else what you have.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were told to meet there at 8 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so our friends took us there, and--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was myself, my brother Paul, my friend Ralph Ginsberg, then my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then there was other people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a famous Danish musician called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
